Observation taxonomy table

observation_metadata_150bp.Rd

This a 975-sample subset of the EMP (Earth Microbiome Project) taxonomy table containing 150bp-length sequences. The samples were picked randomly and evenly across 17 habitats and then evenly across studies in each sample type.

observation_metadata_150bp

Format

Data frame with columns

sequence

Observation-sequence found.

taxonomy1

First taxonomic rank.

taxonomy2

Second taxonomic rank.

taxonomy3

Third taxonomic rank.

taxonomy4

Fourth taxonomic rank.

taxonomy5

Fifth taxonomic rank.

taxonomy6

Sixth taxonomic rank.

taxonomy7

Seventh taxonomic rank.

Source

https://earthmicrobiome.org/
